collectible.name: CV Wearable: Air & Space Vehicles #02 - Jetpack - Concept
collectible.description: With this backpack-sized Jetpack, you'll have fun flying to your friends' houses. Its fuel tank allows it to travel more than 200 kilometers before it needs to be filled, and it has a thermo-reducing implant to keep the fire from burning the skin. There's nothing more unique and sophisticated about portable air vehicles. Created by Gustavo Manute and branded by The Philosopher.
